    <item>
      <title>Git LFS</title>
      <link>/posts/system/development/git-lfs/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>i70170@hotmail.com (Mike Chang)</author>
      <guid>/posts/system/development/git-lfs/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;git-lfs 操作紀錄&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-git-lfs-using-apt&#34; &gt;
&lt;div&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#install-git-lfs-using-apt&#34;&gt;
        #
    &lt;/a&gt;
    Install Git LFS using apt
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo apt install git-lfs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Deprecated; git-lfs 3.x leads to the following error&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ git lfs pull&lt;br&gt;
batch request: Bitbucket cannot execute &amp;lsquo;git-lfs-authenticate &amp;hellip; download&amp;rsquo;. The command is not supported as entered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure you are using a supported SCM, check the syntax and try again.: exit status 1&lt;br&gt;
error: failed to fetch some objects from &amp;lsquo;https://&amp;hellip;/info/lfs&amp;rsquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;暫不詳查原因&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-git-lfs-using-wget&#34; &gt;
&lt;div&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#install-git-lfs-using-wget&#34;&gt;
        #
    &lt;/a&gt;
    Install Git LFS using wget
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ref: &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/git-lfs/git-lfs/releases/tag/v2.13.3&#34;&gt;Github: Git LFS Release v2.13.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;GIT_LFS_VER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;2.13.3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ wget https://github.com/git-lfs/git-lfs/releases/download/v&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$GIT_LFS_VER&lt;/span&gt;/git-lfs-linux-amd64-v&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$GIT_LFS_VER&lt;/span&gt;.tar.gz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ tar -zxvf git-lfs-linux-amd64-v&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$GIT_LFS_VER&lt;/span&gt;.tar.gz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo ./install.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#737994;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# alternatively, install to local user directory&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ vi install.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;prefix&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/home/mike/git-lfs&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ . install.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ vi ~/.bashrc
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db&#34;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/home/mike/git-lfs/bin:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ &lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db&#34;&gt;source&lt;/span&gt; ~/.bashrc
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Initialize Git LFS once&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git lfs install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Pre-commit hook</title>
      <link>/posts/system/development/git-pre-commit/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>i70170@hotmail.com (Mike Chang)</author>
      <guid>/posts/system/development/git-pre-commit/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;使用 pre-commit hook 在建立 commit 時修正撰寫風格並檢查語法&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;從 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Vitaceae/playground/tree/pre-commit&#34;&gt;playground&lt;/a&gt; 搬運過來&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-and-enable-pre-commit&#34; &gt;
&lt;div&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#install-and-enable-pre-commit&#34;&gt;
        #
    &lt;/a&gt;
    Install and enable pre-commit
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ pip install pre-commit
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ pre-commit install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;skip-code-checks&#34; &gt;
&lt;div&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#skip-code-checks&#34;&gt;
        #
    &lt;/a&gt;
    Skip code checks
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;停止 pre-commit hook&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ pre-commit uninstall
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;單次忽略 pre-commit hook&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git commit --no-verify
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
